text: Department of the Treasury Internal Revenue Service
This transmits obsolete IRM 25.7.5, Exempt Organizations/Business Master File Handbook (EO/BMF), Exempt Organizations Extracts and On-Line Programs.

The material relating to Exempt Organizations/Business Master File Handbook EO/BMF Exempt Organizations Extracts and On-Line Programs previously contained in IRM section 25.7.5 is incorporated into IRM 25.7.1, starting at IRM 25.7.1.13, continuing through IRM 25.7.1.14. IRM 25.7.5.1 was merged into IRM 25.7.1.1.
This supersedes and obsoletes IRM 25.7.5, Exempt Organizations/Business Master File Handbook EO/BMF Exempt Organizations Extracts and On-Line Programs, dated January 1, 2020.
Jennifer A. Jett Director, Business Systems Planning Shared Services Tax Exempt and Government Entities
